{"tid":2167382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【飯民大台】肥佬黎不願聽真話，擅改李怡文章！","createTime":"2020-08-21T05:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T11:07:34.000Z","uid":193077,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb05bf40345ba1d65d4d6f0cfb86ab6b1d5e424","tid":2167382,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:33:23.000Z","msg":"被刪一段：<br />\n// 中國文革期間，最盛行的一句毛語錄就是：「凡是敵人反對的我們就要擁護，凡是敵人擁護的我們就要反對。」若以此作行為準則，那就抹煞了「敵人」和「我們」作為「人」的共同需要。「敵人」吃飯，「我們」吃不吃？人們的言行在這句話支配下，社會就變得瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">不幸，這些年香港的民主運動中，也不斷有人用同樣的思維方式去指導言行。往往說怎樣做就中共「最高興」，來肯定自己的反向行為</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n李怡全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/197925030563482/posts/1212964732392835/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F197925030563482%2Fposts%2F1212964732392835%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=0ddf2aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/197925030563482/posts/1212964732392835/</a>"},{"pid":"72f18f6217ac933fedfbc87b416f7f99d438cbc7","tid":2167382,"uid":193077,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"「飯民大台」肥佬黎，真系狗改不了食屎"},{"pid":"668bff76a5072aa3d06bc22809b3f3bdae3ba422","tid":2167382,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc9ff61b83d2f9190629263b0bc886ca903ee69c","tid":2167382,"uid":193077,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"等睇有飯民打手入黎鬧「五毛」、「分化」"},{"pid":"d07e680eeef5f595f0ac1292236d0d05d6c3c98b","tid":2167382,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"乜「凡是敵人反對的我們就要擁護，凡是敵人擁護的我們就要反對。」唔係連動嘅行動綱領嚟嘅咩 <br />\n<br />\n平時非奶共派有人做咗支共港共想佢地做嘅嘢 連登仔就最鍾意用呢句屌鳩佢地架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accf801e27e739221a7e0473748477a5596db4a3","tid":2167382,"uid":193077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote